  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Chapters 1 and 2 are available now in Early Access, offering about 2.5 hours of gameplay. Chapter 3 will become available as a free update at full release.</u></strong> <br> <br>Delve into the depths of Radu Castle's horrors as Dorinela, driven by a desperate plea from the past. This survival horror weaves a tale of trauma and dark secrets, where crafting hideouts becomes your key to staying alive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate an eery gothic castle, listen to immersive voice acting, solve puzzles, and evade a malevolent presence, all while the truth unravels before you. <br> <br><strong>Enter Radu Castle:</strong> Uncover the darkness within.  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882610/extras/146612a973244224599b09b279f53347.poster.avif?t=1770570832\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882610/extras/146612a973244224599b09b279f53347.webm?t=1770570832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882610/extras/146612a973244224599b09b279f53347.mp4?t=1770570832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Build to survive:</strong> Collect resources and build hideouts to evade the malevolent forces. Discover enemies that will force you to strategise how, when and where you build. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882610/extras/84215b857e18f65e4acc4d4f0e34b807.poster.avif?t=1770570832\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882610/extras/84215b857e18f65e4acc4d4f0e34b807.webm?t=1770570832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882610/extras/84215b857e18f65e4acc4d4f0e34b807.mp4?t=1770570832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gripping Narrative:</strong>  A deep, emotional story of trauma and survival, spread over 3 chapters.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882610/extras/52178a0e336e19247984b3f5953bf9c7.poster.avif?t=1770570832\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882610/extras/52178a0e336e19247984b3f5953bf9c7.webm?t=1770570832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882610/extras/52178a0e336e19247984b3f5953bf9c7.mp4?t=1770570832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Puzzles:</strong> Solve puzzles as you explore the hauntingly detailed Radu Castle.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882610/extras/0def31200702ca8935736e3f356b1fe0.poster.avif?t=1770570832\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882610/extras/0def31200702ca8935736e3f356b1fe0.webm?t=1770570832\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2882610/extras/0def31200702ca8935736e3f356b1fe0.mp4?t=1770570832\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
